<%- include('partials/header') -%>

<header class="container">
    <span>there should be a hamburger menu where you can sort by location or event category</span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>also the plan is to verify people's identity through discord, so other discord groups can have their own exclusive events</p>
    <div class="text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <h1><a href="/">Eventer</a></h1>
            <%if(user) {%>
            <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
            <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <%} %>
            <%if(!user) {%>
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
            <%} %>
        </div>
      <span>The #100Devs Event Maker</span>
    </div>
  </header>

<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <span>This is an event maker for all 100Devers. Create or join events. Events can be for professional or social purposes like bowling! Who doesn't like bowling.</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
    <a href="/post/getBrowse" class="col btn btn-primary btn-lg">Browse</a>
    <a href="/post/getCreate" class="col btn btn-primary btn-lg">Create</a>
</div>

<h1 class="d-flex justify-content-center">Trending Events</h1>
<div class="row">
    <%for (let i of topPosts) {%>
        <%console.log(i._id)%>
        <a href="/post/getEvent/<%=i._id%>" class="col-6 border justify-content-row">
        <h5><%=i.title%></h2>
        <div>Caption: <%=i.caption%></div>
        <div>Country: <%=i.country%></div>
        <div>State: <%=i.state%></div>
        <div>City: <%=i.city%></div>
        <div>Date and Time <%=i.dateTime%></div>
        <div><%=i.attending%> Attending</div>
        </a>
    <%}%>
    </div>

<%- include('partials/footer') -%>